<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
<p>
<% if @user.twitter_id %>
  <strong><%= @user.nickname %></strong> ( <a href="<%= @user.twitter_url %>" target="_blank"><%= @user.twitter_url %></a> )
<% else %>
  <strong><%= @user.nickname %></strong> ( <a href="<%= @user.github_url %>" target="_blank"><%= @user.github_url %></a> )
<% end %>
would like to invite you to view the recorded sessions of their <strong><%= @invitation.app.name %></strong> app.<br/>
Personal message from <%= @user.nickname %>: <br/>
<p>
<%= @invitation.message %>
</p>
<br/>
To accept the invitation, please follow the link below:<br/>
<%= link_to @invitation_url, raw(@invitation_url), :target => "_blank" %>
</p>
<p>Thanks!</p>
<p>
  delight.io<br/>
  iOS remote usability testing framework<br/>
  More about us: <a href="http://delight.io" target="_blank">http://delight.io</a><br />
  Follow us on Twitter: <a href="http://twitter.com/delightio" target="_blank">@delightio</a>
</p>
</body>
</html>
